lastfm.summary: "God Break Down The Door" is the fourth track on the 2018 LP Bad Witch. It was first leaked through the official Nine Inch Nails YouTube channel on May 16, 2018 and officially released via all digital outlets and nin.com store on May 17th, 2018. The vocal and musical composition of this song seem to be influenced by David Bowie. In an interview with Zane Lowe, Trent Reznor explained the song's unusual style: "We find if we donâ€™t watch ourselves we tend to try to get somewhere comfortable, because it feels better.
